cs.CV, cs.HC, cs.CY, cs.CL, cs.MM

This paper is primarily focused on machine vision and groundtruth collection, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category. Additionally, the paper discusses the use of a crowdtasking platform (Amazon Mechanical Turk) for groundtruth collection, which relates to human-computer interaction (cs.HC) and cybernetics (cs.CY). The paper also discusses the use of machine learning for training and testing vision systems, which falls under the natural language processing (cs.CL) and multimedia (cs.MM) sub-categories.
